{
  "texts": [
    "We used kernel SHAP to explain various classification models separately, and the factors' importance ranking to each model was reviewed.",
    "Then, we used the proposed ensemble SHAP value to build self-attention transformer models.",
    "Finally, we checked the performance of our proposed models.",
    "Details of the results are shown in the Results section.",
    "ResultsIn this study, we proposed using ensemble SHAP value as knowledge to build self-attention transformer models."
  ]
}